name: UpdateEndpoint
description:
Update an existing endpoint run in a project.

Use this tool to update an existing endpoint run in a specified project with optional parameters.

parameters.name: endpoint_name
parameters.description: The name of the endpoint to be updated. This is a required string parameter.

parameters.name: project_id
parameters.description: Project ID to access the specific project. Obtainable via a call to /api/projects/.

value_schema.description: Project ID of the project you're trying to access. To find the ID of the project, make a call to /api/projects/.

parameters.name: update_endpoint_parameters
parameters.description: A JSON object containing parameters to update the endpoint, such as client_query_id, filters_override, and refresh options.

client_query_id.description: Client provided query ID. Can be used to retrieve the status or cancel the query.
